    en: '"I got it! Let''s turn this around!" Misora shouts to encourage her teammates,
      leading them to a comeback victory despite the fact that she''s not an official
      member of the team. Her innate athletic talent serves her well on the stage
      as well.'
    ja: '「パスカット！　今から逆転してみせるよ！」

