    zh_hant: 眾多青蛙眼花繚亂
  profile:
    en: '"Oooh, they got so many new ones in!" Nana has brought Junna to her usual
      store to look at frog merchandise. Her eyes glitter as she checks out the new
      frogs, while Junna isn''t sure what to make of the odd lineup.'
    ja: '「わあ～、新作グッズ沢山入荷されてる～♪」

      純那に付き合ってもらい、いつものお店にカエルグッズを見に

      訪れたなな。初めて出会ったカエルたちに、瞳を輝かせて品定め。

