    zh_hant: 慶祝料理教室開設♪
  profile:
    en: '"Let''s! Get! Cooking!"

      Nana and Karen head out for some White Day shopping. After they bump into Ichie
      and Fumi, the four girls join up and hold a secret cooking lesson. Wanting to
      record this happy moment, Nana trains her smartphone''s camera on the group.

      "We''re about to kick off our top-secret cooking class♪"'
    ja: '「レッツクッキングだ～☆」

