  profile:
    en: '"...Ugh, I''ve got a fever..." Lying in bed Shiori lets out a feverish sigh.
      "I knew I should have been taking better care of myself..." Shiori, also known
      as Frau Jade, will surely be back to her radiant old self soon.'
    ja: '「……うう、熱出ちゃった……」

