  profile:
    en: '"This time, we will aim high for a ''Renaissance Kobutori Jiisan'' that surpasses
      ''Kobutori Jiisan''!"

      "...Bring it on!"

      Maya and Kaoruko felt the Renaissance''s passion from watching Karen and team
