  profile:
    en: '"The kotatsu is one of the top achievements of Japanese culture, isn''t it?"
      "That''s right." Junna invites Claudine and Maya to join her in the kotatsu
      and is pleased to see them enjoying the experience, complete with mandarin oranges.
