  profile:
    en: '"Got it! Hahh!" Rui''s wooden sword swings down, but Futaba stops it skillfully.
      Futaba is sparring with Rui after being invited to the dojo at Rinmeikan. "Now
      it''s time for my counter!"'
    ja: '「もらった！　はぁっ！」

      裂帛のもと振り下ろされた塁の木刀。

