e Milky Way, the two stars finally embrace each other.\n\"My Orihime...!\"\n\"My Hikoboshi...!\"\n\"I will stay with you until the light of the stars is cast aside by the morning dawn!\"","ja":"１年のうち１日だけ許された逢瀬。天の河原にカササギの橋が架かる時、引き合うふたつの星は手を取り合う。\n「ああ、ああ、僕の織姫……！」\n「私の彦星様……！」\n「朝日で星灯りが消えるまで、君と共に――」","ko":"1년 동안 단 하루만 허락된 만남. 하늘의 강에 까치의 다리가 놓일 때, 서로를 끌어당기는 두 별은 손을 맞잡는다.\n[아아, 아아, 나의 직녀...!]\n[나의 견우 님...!]\n[아침해가 별빛을 지울 때까지, 그대와 함께――]","zh_hant":"每年只被允許相會一日。當喜鵲橋架在天川上時，互相吸引的兩顆星星便可攜起彼此的手。\n『啊…啊…我的織女……！』\n『我的牛郎大人……！』\n『在朝日將繁星光芒覆蓋之前，我只願和你──』"},"published_at":1562223600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000068},"4000069":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101,102],"auto_skill1_id":10066,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":7,"base_hp":150,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":854,"delta_hp":17088,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"ja":"-The LIVE-#2 revival公演記念"},"profile":{"ja":"『少女☆歌劇 レヴュースタァライト -The LIVE-#2 revival』の公演記念メモワールです。"},"published_at":1562569200,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000069},"4000070":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101,102,201,301,401],"auto_skill1_id":10065,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":15,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1708,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"ja":"オールスタァライト配信記念"},"profile":{"ja":"ミニアニメ『少女☆寸劇 オールスタァライト』の配信記念メモワールです。"},"published_at":1562310000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000070},"4000071":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[304,305],"auto_skill1_id":10151,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":210,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":18,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":23924,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":2050,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Summer Holiday","ja":"夏の休日","ko":"여름의 휴일","zh_hant":"夏季的假日"},"profile":{"en":"\"Here's your towel.\"\n\"Thank you.\"\nFive friends are visiting the pool. Two of them are resting after having a swim. The other three are still full of energy.\n\"Heh heh, they look like they're having fun!\"\n\"Shall we join them, Shizuha?\"\nFive friends enjoy their summer to the fullest!","ja":"「はい、タオル」\n「ありがとう」\n５人でやってきたプール。ひと泳ぎしたふたりは休憩中。\nでも、他の３人はまだまだ元気いっぱいで……\n「ふふ、みんな楽しそう」\n「私たちも行こっか、静羽！」\nさあ、夏を心ゆくまで楽しもう！","ko":"[자, 여기 수건]\n[고마워]\n5명이서 찾아온 수영장. 2명은 헤엄친 후 휴식 중.\n하지만, 다른 3명은 아직 기운이 넘쳐서...\n[후후, 모두 즐거워 보여]\n[우리들도 갈까, 시즈하!]\n자, 여름을 마음껏 즐기자!","zh_hant":"「來，毛巾」\n「謝謝」\n5個人來到了游泳池。其中2人遊完一圈正在休息。\n然而，其他3人仍非常有精神......\n｢呵呵，大家看起來都很開心｣\n「我們也過去吧，靜羽！」\n來吧，盡情享受夏天！"},"published_at":1563260400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000071},"4000072":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[202],"auto_skill1_id":20028,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Ichie's Cool Hospitality☆","ja":"いちえのクールなおもてなし☆","ko":"이치에의 쿨한 대접☆","zh_hant":"一愛的冰涼涼招待☆"},"profile":{"en":"\"Alright, I'll do my best☆\" Thinking of everyone in Rinmeikan, Ichie turns the handle. There's still time until summer, though. \"It's almost time for ice-cold shaved ice!\" Will they like the syrup that goes with it?","ja":"「よぉ～し、がんばるぞぉ～☆」\n凛明館のみんなのために、いちえはハンドルを回す。\n夏本番はまだ少し先だけど。\n「そろそろキンキンのかき氷が恋しい季節でしょ〜」\n用意したシロップ、気に入ってもらえるかな？","ko":"[좋았어~, 힘내자~☆]\n린메이칸 친구들을 위해 이치에는 핸들을 돌린다.\n진짜 여름은 아직 조금 멀었지만.\n[슬슬 차가운 빙수가 당기는 계절이잖아~]\n준비한 시럽은 다들 마음에 들어할까?","zh_hant":"「好～我要加油囉～☆」\n為了凜明館的大家，一愛開始轉動把手。\n雖然還不到那麼熱。\n「大家也差不多該懷念綿密的刨冰了吧〜」\n我準備的糖漿，大家會不會喜歡呢？"},"published_at":1563260400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000072},"4000073":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[103,106,107],"auto_skill1_id":10096,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":7,"base_hp":150,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":854,"delta_hp":17088,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Synchro Girls!","ja":"シンクロガールズ！","ko":"싱크로 걸즈!","zh_hant":"水上芭蕾女孩！"},"profile":{"en":"\"Synchro Girls\" is an in-the-water play that follows a synchronized swimming team and their fight to save their public pool. The Stage Girls' heated summer begins with their declaration to save their beloved local \"Shiratori Pool\"! - From \"Shiratori Public Pool\" & \"Seisho Music Academy\" 100-Year Anniversary Special Combined Performance \"Synchro Girls\"","ja":"村営プールの危機に立ち上がったシンクロ部の奮闘を描く、水上舞台『シンクロガールズ』。\nみんなが愛する村営『白鳥プール』を守る為に、少女たちの熱い夏が始まる……！\n『市営しらとりプール』『聖翔音楽学園』１００周年特別共同公演『シンクロガールズ』より。","ko":"마을 수영장의 위기에 들고일어난 싱크로부의 분투를 그리는, 수상무대 [싱크로 걸즈].\n모두가 사랑하는 마을의 [시라토리 수영장]을 지키기 위해, 소녀들의 뜨거운 여름이 시작된다...!\n―[시립 시라토리 수영장], [세이쇼 음악학교] 100주년 특별 공동 공연 [싱크로 걸즈]로부터.","zh_hant":"描述為拯救村營泳池危機而挺身而出的水上芭蕾社奮鬥故事：水上舞台劇『水上芭蕾女孩』。\n為了守護大家心愛的村營「天鵝泳池」，少女們的熱血夏季即將開幕……！\n─源自「市營白鵠泳池」與「聖翔音樂學院」100週年紀念特別公演。"},"published_at":1564038000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000073},"4000074":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[201],"auto_skill1_id":10100,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":30,"base_pdef":30,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":3417,"delta_pdef":3417,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Tamao's Summer Preparations","ja":"珠緒の夏支度","ko":"타마오의 여름 준비","zh_hant":"珠緒準備迎接夏天"},"profile":{"en":"\"The breeze is good, so here is perfect.\" Tamao puts up the decoration by the window of the dorm's shared space. The windchime that everyone picked together rings clear and bright. It'll definitely bring about a refreshing coolness.","ja":"「ここなら風も良く通るし、ちょうどいいかな？」\n寮のコミュニティスペースで窓辺を飾る珠緒。\nみんなと選んだお気に入りの風鈴は、軽やかに澄んだ音色を響かせる。\nきっと爽やかな涼しさを運んでくれることだろう。","ko":"[여기는 바람도 잘 통하니까 딱 좋을 것 같은데?]\n기숙사의 커뮤니티 스페이스에서 창가를 꾸미는 타마오.\n다 함께 고른, 마음에 쏙 드는 풍경은 경쾌하고 맑은 음색을 낸다.\n분명 기분 좋은 시원함을 전해 줄 것이다.","zh_hant":"「這邊很通風，應該剛剛好吧？」\n珠緒在宿舍交誼廳的窗邊裝飾著風鈴。\n大家一起選的風鈴，響出輕快的悅耳音色。\n它一定會為大家帶來一絲涼爽的氣息吧。"},"published_at":1563346800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000074},"4000075":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[201,204],"auto_skill1_id":10088,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":15,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1708,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Urashima Taro Performance Flyer","ja":"「浦島太郎」公演のお知らせ","ko":"[우라시마 타로] 공연 안내","zh_hant":"「浦島太郎」公演通告"},"profile":{"en":"The turtle brought the kind boy to Ryugu-jo, the castle where the beautiful princess resides. Among the colorful fish underwater, their feelings for each other intermingle. Look forward to Rinmeikan Girls School Performance Department's Urashima Taro!","ja":"心優しき青年が亀に連れられやってきたのは\n美しき姫が住まう竜宮城――。\n極彩色の魚たちが舞う海底で、\nふたりは泡沫の時を過ごし、\nお伽噺にはない、淡い想いが交錯する。\n凛明館女学校演劇科の公演に、乞うご期待！","ko":"마음씨 상냥한 청년이 거북이에게 이끌려 도착한 곳은\n아름다운 공주가 사는 용궁――.\n화려한 물고기들이 춤추는 바다 밑에서\n두 사람은 물거품 같은 시간을 보내고\n동화에서는 없었던 아련한 마음이 교차한다.\n린메이칸 여학교 연극과 공연을 기대해 주세요!","zh_hant":"心地善良的青年被帶往的地方是\n美麗公主所居住的龍宮城──\n在七彩繽紛的魚兒們舞動的海底，\n兩人度過了夢一般的時光。\n一段童話中未描寫到的淡淡思念互相交錯著。\n凜明館女子學校 戲劇科公演，敬請期待！"},"published_at":1564988400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000075},"4000076":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[201],"auto_skill1_id":10152,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":15,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1708,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Lured by Festival Music","ja":"祭囃子に誘われて","ko":"축제 음악에 이끌려","zh_hant":"日式祭典樂的邀請"},"profile":{"en":"\"Don't get lost, okay?\"\nShe hurries her pace and gets in line next to her.\n\"Where shall we go next?\"\nSo many choices - the shooting game, candy apples...\nThe summer festival has just begun.","ja":"「迷子にならないでくださいね？」\nその姿を見失わないように、足を早めて隣に並ぶ。\n「次はどの屋台にしましょうか」\n射的？　それともリンゴ飴？\n夏祭りは、まだ始まったばかり。","ko":"[미아가 되지 말아 주세요?]\n그 모습을 놓치지 않도록 잰걸음으로 옆에 나란히 선다.\n[다음은 어느 노점에 갈까요]\n사격? 아니면 사과 사탕?\n여름축제는 아직 막 시작된 참.","zh_hant":"「不要走散囉？」\n為了不要讓那身姿消失到視線外，我趕緊走到她身旁。\n「接下來要去哪個攤販呢？」\n打靶？還是糖葫蘆？\n夏日的祭典現在才要開始。"},"published_at":1565766000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000076},"4000077":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[404,405],"auto_skill1_id":28051,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":15,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1708,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Poolside Incident","ja":"プールサイド・ハプニング","ko":"풀 사이드 해프닝","zh_hant":"泳池邊小劇場"},"profile":{"en":"\"Eek! Yachiyo-senpai...!\" \"We can't lose this chance!\" Yachiyo and Shiori relax by the poolside. Shiori panics as Yachiyo hugs her. \"Tighter!\" \"Senpai, you're too close...!\"","ja":"「はわわっ！？　やちよ先輩、いきなり何を……っ」\n「だってせっかくの記念撮影だよ〜？」\nプールサイドのやちよと栞。\nカメラの前でハグされた栞は大慌て。\n「もっとくっつこうよ〜」\n「かか、顔が近いですぅ……！」","ko":"[으와아앗!? 야치요 선배, 갑자기 뭘 하는... 윽]\n[그치만 모처럼 기념 촬영인걸~?]\n풀 사이드의 야치요와 시오리.\n[카메라 앞에서 허그당한 시오리는 허둥지둥.\n[좀 더 들러붙자구~]\n[어, 얼굴이 가까워요~...!]","zh_hant":"「哇啊啊！？八千代學姐妳怎麼突然……？」\n「難得的紀念照片耶～？」\n泳池邊的八千代與栞。\n在相機前突然被抱住的栞驚嚇一百點。\n「再靠近一點嘛～」\n「臉、臉、臉太近了……！」"},"published_at":1565766000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000077},"4000078":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101,102,201,301,401],"auto_skill1_id":10063,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":9,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":18,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":0,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1025,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":2050,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"ja":"みんなでお出迎え！"},"profile":{"ja":"『東武動物公園』とのコラボ開催記念メモワールです。"},"published_at":1567839600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000078},"4000079":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101],"auto_skill1_id":20027,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":210,"base_mdef":18,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":0,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":23924,"delta_mdef":2050,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"ja":"『戦姫絶唱シンフォギアAXZ』衣裳"},"profile":{"ja":"中国拳法の構えで颯爽とシンフォギアを着こなす華恋。\n「私も響ちゃんみたいに格好良くきめるぞ～！……『この拳もッ！…命もッ！…シンフォギアだッ！！』」"},"published_at":1568098800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000079},"4000080":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101,103],"auto_skill1_id":15027,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Back to the Renaissance 2019","ja":"『遥かなるルネサンス・２０１９』","ko":"[머나먼 르네상스 2019]","zh_hant":"『遙遠的文藝復興・２０１９』"},"profile":{"en":"In the Basic Theatre Theory II class, Karen, Hikari, and Mahiru act out the most difficult script of all time — \"Back to the Renaissance\"\n\n\"Alright, let's do this! It's our Renaissance!\"\n\"Now that we're ready, we'll put on a fantastic Renaissance for sure!\"\nAnd the finished performance is...!?","ja":"基礎演劇概論Ⅱの授業で華恋・ひかり・まひるの三人が演じるのは、歴代で最も難関な脚本と言われる『遥かなるルネサンス』！\n\n「よーし、じゃあやろう！　私たちのルネサンス！」\n「今の私たちなら、きっとすごいルネサンス間違いなしだよ！」\nそうして出来上がった舞台とは……！？","ko":"기초연극개론II 수업에서 카렌·히카리·마히루 세 사람이 연기하는 작품은 역대 가장 난관의 각본이라 불리는 [머나먼 르네상스]!\n\n[좋~았어, 그럼 해보자! 우리들의 르네상스!]\n[지금의 우리라면 분명 굉장한 르네상스가 될게 틀림없어!]\n그리고 완성된 무대란...?!","zh_hant":"在基礎戲劇概論Ⅱ的課程中，華戀、光、真晝三人將挑戰演出公認歷屆最難演的劇本『遙遠的文藝復興』！\n\n「好，來吧！　我們的文藝復興！」\n「現在的我們一定能夠演出最棒的文藝復興！」\n在這樣的情況下誕生的舞台結果是……！？"},"published_at":1567666800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000080},"4000081":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[302,303],"auto_skill1_id":10153,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":15,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":1708,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Moon Viewing","ja":"それぞれのお月見","ko":"각자의 달구경","zh_hant":"賞月百百種"},"profile":{"en":"Different people enjoy viewing the autumn moon in different ways.\n\"I love singing! Moon bunny, moon bunny! Where are you hopping to?\"\nLalafin merrily sings, while Misora...\n\"I love eating fall delicacies!\"\nMisora enjoys delicious autumnal treats!","ja":"お月見の楽しみ方は人それぞれ。\n「お月見って歌いたくなるよね！\nうさぎ、うさぎ♪　なに見て跳ねる♪」\n楽しく歌うララフィン。一方、美空は――。\n「お月見って美味しいですよね！」\n秋の味覚にご満悦！","ko":"달구경을 즐기는 법은 사람마다 다른 법.\n[달구경이라니 노래하고 싶어져!\n토끼, 토끼야♪ 뭘 보고 뛰느냐♪]\n즐겁게 노래하는 라라핀. 한편, 미소라는――.\n[달구경은 참 맛있네요!]\n가을의 미각을 만끽!","zh_hant":"每個人都有不同的賞月方式。\n「賞月就會想唱歌嘛！\n兔子、兔子♪看著什麼跳啊跳♪」\n比起開心唱著歌的菈樂菲，在一旁的美空則是──\n「賞月就是要吃好吃的！」\n說到秋天就是食慾之秋！"},"published_at":1565766000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000081},"4000082":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[303,305],"auto_skill1_id":15017,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Sailor's Call","ja":"Sailor's Call","ko":"Sailor's Call","zh_hant":"Sailor's Call"},"profile":{"en":"The time given to the sailors is a mere 24 hours. They're making every effort to find his first love in the port town! \"Marion! Look! \"That's...!\" With the clock ticking away, what will happen to the young sailor captain's love...!?","ja":"水兵たちに与えられた時間はたった２４時間。\n初恋の人捜しのために港町を奔走する！\n「マリオン！　見て！」\n「あれは……！」\n刻一刻とタイムリミットが迫る中、\n若き水兵長の恋の行方は……！？","ko":"수병들에게 주어진 시간은 겨우 24시간.\n첫사랑 상대를 찾기 위해 항구도시를 열심히 뛰어다닌다!\n[마리온! 봐!]\n[저건...!]\n시시각각 시간 제한이 다가오는 가운데,\n젊은 수병장의 사랑은 어디로...!? ","zh_hant":"海軍士兵被賦予的時間僅有24小時。\n為了尋找初戀對象而在海港小鎮中四處奔走！\n「馬里翁！你看！」\n「那是……！」\n所剩時間一分一秒地流去，\n年輕海軍士兵長的戀情究竟會……！？"},"published_at":1569394800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000082},"4000083":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[303],"auto_skill1_id":15032,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Time is Money!","ja":"時は金なりを実践中！","ko":"시간은 금이라는 말을 실천 중!","zh_hant":"馬上實踐「時間就是金錢」！"},"profile":{"en":"\"Hurry! Zoom!\" I won't waste a single second today! Lalafin charges with a strong determination. She'll definitely fulfill the schedule that she'd spent a lot of time coming up with! When it's accomplished, she'll understand the importance of time for sure!","ja":"「急げっ！　びゅーんっ！」\n今日は１秒だって無駄にしない！\n強い決意を胸に、駆けるララフィン。\nいっぱい考えて作ったスケジュール、絶対達成してみせるよ！\nやり遂げた時、きっと時間の大切さがわかるから！","ko":"[서둘러! 피융~!]\n오늘은 1초라도 낭비하지 않겠어!\n강한 결의를 가슴에 담고 달리는 라라핀.\n열심히 생각해서 만든 스케줄이니 꼭 달성하고 말겠어!\n달성했을 때 분명 시간의 소중함을 알 수 있을 테니까!","zh_hant":"「快點！　咻～！」\n今天一分一秒都不能浪費！\n菈樂菲抱著強烈的決心奔跑著。\n絕對要完成努力想出來的行程表！\n結束後，一定能夠了解到時間的重要性！"},"published_at":1569740400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000083},"4000084":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[305],"auto_skill1_id":15042,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Stage Girls Don't Know Compromise","ja":"舞台少女は妥協を知らない","ko":"무대소녀는 타협을 모른다","zh_hant":"舞台少女從不妥協"},"profile":{"en":"Putting on the costume and expressing the happiness of going ashore and the puzzlement of feeling dizzy from being on land after a long time. \"This way expresses it better...!\" Shizuha's inquisitive mind knows no boundaries ― she continues to dance until she's satisfied.","ja":"役の衣裳を身に着けて陸に上がった喜びと、久々の陸に酔ってしまった戸惑いを全身で表現する。\n「こっちのほうが伝わるはず……！」\n静羽の探究心はとどまることを知らず、納得の行くまで彼女は踊り続ける。","ko":"배역의 의상을 입고, 육지에 올라선 기쁨과 오랜만에 디딘 육지에서 땅 멀미를 하고 느낀 당혹감을 전신으로 표현한다.\n[이렇게 하는 편이 더 잘 전해질 거야...!]\n시즈하의 탐구심은 그칠 줄 모르고, 납득이 갈 때까지 그녀는 계속해서 춤춘다.","zh_hant":"穿上角色的服裝，用盡全身來表現出登陸後的喜悅，以及沉醉在久違的陸地上的困惑。\n「這種方式應該比較能夠傳達......！」\n靜羽不停地跳著舞，她將持續探求直到自己滿意為止。"},"published_at":1569740400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000084},"4000085":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[109],"auto_skill1_id":15052,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"Halloween Through the Glass","ja":"ガラス越しのハロウィン","ko":"유리창 너머의 할로윈","zh_hant":"玻璃對面的萬聖節"},"profile":{"en":"When autumn comes, the city turns into Halloween colors. \"Sweets in such gaudy colors are nice once in a while.\" She thinks about this year's Halloween while gazing at the colorful sweets in the shop window. ","ja":"秋めいてくると、街はハロウィン一色。\n「こういうどぎつい色のお菓子も、たまにはええどすなぁ」\nショーウィンドウに並ぶカラフルなスイーツを見つめながら、今年のハロウィンに思いを馳せる。","ko":"가을이 깊어지면 거리는 할로윈 일색이다.\n[이런 칙칙한 색의 과자도 때로는 괜찮네요]\n쇼윈도에 전시된 칼라풀한 디저트들을 바라보면서 올해 할로윈 생각을 한다.","zh_hant":"秋意到來後，街道上也充滿萬聖節的氣氛。\n「這種色彩強烈的零食，偶爾吃吃也不錯」\n看著展示窗裡陳列的色彩繽紛糖果，開始思考著今年的萬聖節。"},"published_at":1570172400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000085},"4000086":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101,102,103,104,105,106,107,108,109],"auto_skill1_id":16002,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"(1st Anniv.) Seisho Music Academy","ja":"[１周年] 聖翔音楽学園","ko":"[1주년] 세이쇼 음악학교","zh_hant":"[1週年] 聖翔音樂學院"},"profile":{"en":"Nine friends from Seisho Music Academy Actor Training Department 99th Class share the stage to each become a top star! ","ja":"聖翔音楽学園 俳優育成科 ９９期生の９人は舞台に立つ。あの星を目指して！","ko":"세이쇼 음악학교 배우육성과 99기생 9명은 무대에 선다. 저 별을 목표로!","zh_hant":"聖翔音樂學院演員養成科99期生的9人站上舞台。目標成為那顆星！"},"published_at":1571382000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000086},"4000087":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[401,402,403,404,405],"auto_skill1_id":16017,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"(1st Anniv.) Siegfeld Institute of Music","ja":"[１周年] シークフェルト音楽学院","ko":"[1주년] 시크펠트 음악학원","zh_hant":"[1週年] 席格菲特音樂學院"},"profile":{"en":"Five Edels from Siegfeld Institute of Music Acting Department share the stage. All for the king!","ja":"シークフェルト音楽学院 舞台俳