aterial_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"XII Hanged Man [Reverse]","ja":"XII 吊られた男【逆位置】","ko":"XII 매달린 사람[역위치]","zh_hant":"XII 倒吊人【逆位】"},"profile":{"en":"Wasted Efforts, Fool’s Errand","ja":"徒労、骨折り損","ko":"헛수고, 보람 없음","zh_hant":"徒勞無功、白費心力"},"published_at":1627282800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000163},"4000164":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[104],"auto_skill1_id":28080,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Claudine Saijo","ja":"【Star of the day】西條クロディーヌ","ko":"[Star of the day] 사이조 클로딘","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】西條克洛迪娜"},"profile":{"en":"\"I-I look dashing? Why, merci!\" Today is a special day for Claudine. From Edward Teach to Black Lion Nation Knight, and many more—each and every performance is important for her. Stage Girl Claudine Saijo—getting better day by day!","ja":"「とってもキレイ、ですって？　ふふっ、merci」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\nエドワード・ティーチ、黒獅子の国の騎士……and more.\nたくさんの舞台の思い出を抱き、舞台少女西條クロディーヌは日々進化中。","ko":"[너무나 아름답다고? 후훗, merci]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n에드워드 티치, 흑사자 나라의 기사... and more.\n수많은 무대의 추억을 안고 무대소녀 사이조 클로딘은 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「你說我很漂亮？呵呵，merci（謝謝）」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n愛德華·蒂奇、黑獅子之國騎士……and more.\n懷抱著眾多的舞台回憶，舞台少女西條克洛迪娜天天進化中。"},"published_at":1627743600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000164},"4000165":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[305],"auto_skill1_id":28095,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Shizuha Kocho","ja":"【Star of the day】胡蝶静羽","ko":"[Star of the day] 코쵸 시즈하","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】胡蝶靜羽"},"profile":{"en":"\"Thank you for your wishes. I think I'll let myself be pampered just for today!\" Today is a special day for Shizuha. From Sailor Captain Marion to Pirate Queen, and many more—each and every performance is important for her. Stage Girl Shizuha Kocho—getting better day by day!","ja":"「お祝いありがとう。今日だけは、みんなに甘えちゃおうかしら」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\n水兵長マリオン、海賊女王……and more.\nたくさんの舞台の思い出を抱き、舞台少女胡蝶静羽は日々進化中。","ko":"[축하해줘서 고마워. 오늘만큼은 모두에게 응석을 부려볼까?]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n수병장 마리온, 해적 여왕... and more.\n수많은 무대의 추억을 안고 무대소녀 코쵸 시즈하는 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「謝謝大家的祝福！今天就讓我依賴一下大家吧」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n海軍士兵長馬里翁、海盜女王……and more.\n懷抱著眾多的舞台回憶，舞台少女胡蝶靜羽天天進化中。"},"published_at":1629039600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000165},"4000166":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[502],"auto_skill1_id":28102,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Suzu Minase","ja":"【Star of the day】南風涼","ko":"[Star of the day] 미나세 스즈","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】南風涼"},"profile":{"en":"\"Thank you for celebrating my birthday! I will grow even further!\" Today is a special day for Suzu. From working behind the scenes to working on stage – her heart is filled with expectations for the next stage. Stage Girl Suzu Minase – getting better day by day!","ja":"「みんな、お祝いありがとー！　アタシの成長に乞うご期待！」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\n裏方として、役者として――これから創り上げるたくさんの舞台への期待を胸に、舞台少女南風涼は日々進化中。","ko":"[다들 축하해줘서 고마워~! 내가 성장해 나가는 걸 기대해 줘!]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n스태프로서, 배우로서―― 앞으로 만들어나갈 수많은 무대에 대한 기대를 안고 무대소녀 미나세 스즈는 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「謝謝各位的祝福！請好好期待我今後的成長吧！」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n不論是作為幕後人員，還是演員——將今後也要持續創作舞台的期待收納於心，舞台少女南風涼天天進化中。"},"published_at":1629903600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000166},"4000167":{"active_skill_id":26,"appearance_chara_ids":[302],"auto_skill1_id":20020,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":113,"base_hp":445,"base_mdef":363,"base_pdef":363,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":3000,"delta_hp":45000,"delta_mdef":3000,"delta_pdef":3000,"has_alternative_image":1,"material_ex