elta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Peach Oath","ja":"桃園の誓い","ko":"도원의 맹세","zh_hant":"桃園三結義"},"profile":{"en":"\"The three of us may have been born with different surnames, yet we have come together as brothers!\"\n Liu Bei, Guan Yu and Zhang Fei take an oath to protect the nation, and lead the people.\nUnder peach trees in full bloom, the three of them become sworn brothers.","ja":"「我ら３人！　生まれた時は違えども！　ここに義兄弟の契りを結ぶ！」\n国を憂い、民を導く英雄を志す劉備に賛同する張飛と関羽。\n満開の桃園で、３人は固く誓い合い、運命と共にする覚悟を決める。","ko":"[우리 셋! 비록 태어난 날은 다르지만! 여기서 의형제를 맺는다!]\n나라를 근심하여 백성을 이끄는 영웅에 뜻을 두는 유비와 그에게 찬동하는 장비와 관우.\n세 사람은 만개한 복숭아밭에서 굳은 맹세를 하며 운명을 함께 할 각오를 다진다.","zh_hant":"「我們三人！雖生而為異姓！也要在此結為兄弟！」\n憂國憂民的劉備，立志要成為領導人民的英雄。張飛與關羽則對此非常贊同。\n三人在桃花盛開的桃園中立下了堅固的誓言，決心與彼此共存亡。"},"published_at":1629788400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000177},"4000178":{"active_skill_id":41,"appearance_chara_ids":[402],"auto_skill1_id":20020,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":113,"base_hp":445,"base_mdef":363,"base_pdef":363,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":3000,"delta_hp":45000,"delta_mdef":3000,"delta_pdef":3000,"has_alternative_image":1,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Ⅴ Hierophant [Upright]","ja":"V 法王【正位置】","ko":"V 교황 [정위치]","zh_hant":"V 教皇【正位】"},"profile":{"en":"Compassion, Empathy","ja":"広い視野、共感、慈愛","ko":"넓은 시야, 공감, 자애","zh_hant":"寬廣的視野、共鳴、慈愛"},"published_at":1630998000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000178},"4000179":{"active_skill_id":33,"appearance_chara_ids":[402],"auto_skill1_id":10080,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":105,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":5000,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":1,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Ⅴ Hierophant [Reverse]","ja":"V 法王【逆位置】","ko":"V 교황 [역위치]","zh_hant":"V 教皇【逆位】"},"profile":{"en":"Narrow Perspective, Misunderstanding, Opposition","ja":"狭い視野、誤解、反感","ko":"좁은 시야, 오해, 반감","zh_hant":"狹隘的視野、誤解、反感"},"published_at":1630998000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id