_ids":[103,903],"auto_skill1_id":10080,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":105,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":0,"cost":12,"delta_atk":5000,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Cleaning Together","ja":"一緒にお掃除","ko":"다 같이 청소","zh_hant":"一起大掃除"},"profile":{"en":"\"Scrub until it sparkles, and spin♪\"\nKaren, Hikari, and Mahiru are rehearsing with Sakura, Erica, and Gemini for the \"New Urashima Taro Contest\".\nWhen it's over, they tidy up together.\nGemini's graceful mopping skills surprise even Mahiru.","ja":"「キュキュッと磨いてー、ここでターン！」\n『新説・浦島太郎コンクール』に向け、一緒に練習するようになった華恋・ひかり・まひるとさくら・エリカ・ジェミニ。\n練習終わりのお掃除もみんなで取り組むことに。\nジェミニの華麗なモップさばきに、まひるも思わずノリノリに。","ko":"[뽀득뽀득 닦고~, 여기서 턴!]\n[신설 우라시마 타로 콩쿠르]를 앞두고 함께 연습하게 된 카렌, 히카리, 마히루와 사쿠라, 에리카, 제미니.\n연습 후 청소도 다 같이 하기로 한다.\n제미니의 화려한 대걸레질에 마히루도 저절로 신이 난다.","zh_hant":"「仔細地拖乾淨後，在這裡來個收尾！」\n為了『新說・浦島太郎大賽』而一起練習的華戀、光、真晝及櫻、艾莉卡和潔蜜妮。\n結束練習後一同認真地打掃。\n潔蜜妮那華麗的拖把使用技巧，讓真晝也忍不住躍躍欲試。"},"published_at":1631775600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000182},"4000183":{"active_skill_id":44,"appearance_chara_ids":[102,901],"auto_skill1_id":22394,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":168,"base_pdef":168,"can_use_limitbreak_item":0,"cost":12,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":8000,"delta_pdef":8000,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Rare Co-star","ja":"希代の共演","ko":"희대의 합동 공연","zh_hant":"稀世的共演"},"profile":{"en":"\"...Are you really...going back?\"\n\"We show our emotions, and burn our souls... If we stand together, we could shine so much!\"\nSparks fly as the brilliance of Sakura and the others clash on the special stage.","ja":"「……――本当に、戻ってしまうの？」\n「こうやって互いの想いをぶつけ、魂を燃やしあう……私たちが一緒なら、こんなにもキラめけるのに！！」\n互いのキラめきに心を燃やしあう特別なステージで、さくらたちと火花を散らす。","ko":"[...――정말 돌아가는 거야?]\n[이렇게 서로의 마음을 부딪쳐 영혼을 불태우는... 우리가 함께라면 이토록 반짝일 수 있는데!!]\n서로의 반짝임에 마음을 불태우는 특별한 스테이지에서 사쿠라 일행과 불꽃을 튀긴다.","zh_hant":"「……真的要回去嗎？」\n「我們已經坦誠相見，燃燒彼此的靈魂……明明只要我們在一起，就能發出那麼耀眼的光芒！！」\n在以彼此的光芒燃燒彼此的心的特別舞台上，她們與櫻等人互相碰撞、火花四濺。"},"published_at":1631775600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000183},"4000184":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[101],"auto_skill1_id":28077,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Karen Aijo","ja":"【Star of the day】愛城華恋","ko":"[Star of the day] 아이조 카렌","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】愛城華戀"},"profile":{"en":"\"Thank you for celebrating with me, everyone! It's such a wonderful day!\" Today is a special day for Karen. From Vampire to Sherlock Holmes, and many more—each and every performance is important for her. Stage Girl Karen Aijo—getting better day by day!","ja":"「みんなお祝いありがとう！　ぐっどぐっどですよ～！」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\nアーサー、シャーロック・ホームズ……and more.\nたくさんの舞台の思い出を抱き、舞台少女愛城華恋は日々進化中。","ko":"[다들 축하해 줘서 고마워! 굿굿이에요~!]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n아서, 셜록 홈즈... and more.\n수많은 무대의 추억을 안고 무대소녀 아이조 카렌은 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「謝謝大家的祝福！很Good Good喔～！」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n亞瑟王、夏洛克･福爾摩斯……and more.\n懷抱著眾多的舞台回憶，舞台少女愛城華戀天天進化中。"},"published_at":1632668400,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000184},"4000185":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[106],"auto_skill1_id":28082,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Junna Hoshimi","ja":"【Star of the day】星見純那","ko":"[Star of the day] 호시미 준나","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】星見純那"},"profile":{"en":"\"I-I look cute...? *pout* Stop teasing me!\" Today is a special day for Junna. From Knight of the Black Lion Nation to Christine, and many more—each and every performance is important for her. Stage Girl Junna Hoshimi—getting better day by day!","ja":"「えっ、かわいい……？　もう、茶化さないでよ、照れるじゃない」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\n黒獅子の国の騎士、クリスティーヌ……and more.\nたくさんの舞台の思い出を抱き、舞台少女星見純那は日々進化中。","ko":"[뭐, 귀엽다고...? 뭐야, 놀리지 마, 쑥스럽잖아]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n흑사자 나라의 기사, 크리스틴... and more.\n수많은 무대의 추억을 안고 무대소녀 호시미 준나는 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「咦，你說我很可愛……？別捉弄我了，我會害羞的」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n黑獅子之國騎士、克莉絲汀……and more.\n懷抱著眾多的舞台回憶，舞台少女星見純那天天進化中。"},"published_at":1633014000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000185},"4000186":{"active_skill_id":0,"appearance_chara_ids":[302],"auto_skill1_id":28092,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":30,"base_hp":300,"base_mdef":50,"base_pdef":50,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":9,"delta_atk":3417,"delta_hp":34177,"delta_mdef":5696,"delta_pdef":5696,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":500,"name":{"en":"[Star of the day] Misora Kano","ja":"【Star of the day】叶美空","ko":"[Star of the day] 카노 미소라","zh_hant":"【Star of the day】葉美空"},"profile":{"en":"\"I haven't wore something so formal since I was a kid.\" Today is a special day for Misora. From White Rabbit to Greenhorn Helmsman, and many more—each and every performance is important for her. Stage Girl Misora Kano—getting better day by day!","ja":"「こんな格好、七五三以来でなんだか照れくさいですね」\n今日はとっても特別な日。\n白うさぎ、駆け出し操舵士……and more.\nたくさんの舞台の思い出を抱き、舞台少女叶美空は日々進化中。","ko":"[이런 복장은 어릴 때 이후로 처음이라 쑥스럽네요]\n오늘은 무척 특별한 날.\n흰토끼, 신출내기 조타수... and more.\n수많은 무대의 추억을 안고 무대소녀 카노 미소라는 나날이 진화 중.","zh_hant":"「七五三節過後我就沒再穿過這種服裝了，真令人害羞呢」\n今天是非常特別的日子。\n白兔、新星掌舵手……and more.\n懷抱著眾多的舞台回憶，舞台少女葉美空天天進化中。"},"published_at":1633791600,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000186},"4000187":{"active_skill_id":13,"appearance_chara_ids":[401,402],"auto_skill1_id":10080,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":105,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":0,"base_pdef":0,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":5000,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":0,"delta_pdef":0,"has_alternative_image":0,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"Enchanting Spicy Curry","ja":"魅惑のスパイシーカレー","ko":"매혹의 스파이시 카레","zh_hant":"魅惑的辣味咖哩"},"profile":{"en":"\"Akira, today's curry smells different than usual.\"\n\"Keen as always, Michiru. I used a new special chili sauce today.\"\nAkira calmly enjoys her brutally spicy curry for lunch with Michiru. They take a much earned break before the afternoon rehearsals.","ja":"「晶、今日のカレーいつもと香りが違うね。」\n「さすがだな、ミチル。今日は新作のカレー用特製チリソースを使ったんだ。」\nむせ返りそうな激辛カレーを前に平然とランチを楽しむ晶とミチル。\n午後のレッスンに向け、束の間の休息を満喫するのだった。","ko":"[아키라, 오늘 카레 평소랑 냄새가 다르네.]\n[역시 미치루야. 오늘은 신작 카레용 특제 칠리소스를 사용했어.]\n보기만 해도 기침이 날 것 같은 아주 매운 카레를 앞에 두고 태연하게 점심 식사를 즐기는 아키라와 미치루.\n오후 레슨에 대비해 잠깐 동안의 휴식을 만끽하고 있다.","zh_hant":"「晶，今天的咖哩跟平時的香味不一樣呢。」\n「真不愧是未知留。今天新做的咖哩可是用了特製辣椒醬喔。」\n面對這看起來非常嗆鼻的激辣咖哩，晶和未知留卻若無其事地享用著午餐。\n兩人享受了這短暫的休息，為下午的練習養精蓄銳。"},"published_at":1633014000,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000187},"4000188":{"active_skill_id":45,"appearance_chara_ids":[305],"auto_skill1_id":22394,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":113,"base_hp":445,"base_mdef":363,"base_pdef":363,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":3000,"delta_hp":45000,"delta_mdef":3000,"delta_pdef":3000,"has_alternative_image":1,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"XX Judgement [Upright]","ja":"XX 審判【正位置】","ko":"XX 심판[정위치]","zh_hant":"XX 審判【正位】"},"profile":{"en":"Development, Awakening, Rebirth","ja":"発展、覚醒、再生産","ko":"발전, 각성, 재생산","zh_hant":"發展、覺醒、再生產"},"published_at":1633330800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000188},"4000189":{"active_skill_id":48,"appearance_chara_ids":[305],"auto_skill1_id":12168,"auto_skill1_type":1,"base_atk":0,"base_hp":0,"base_mdef":168,"base_pdef":168,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":0,"delta_hp":0,"delta_mdef":8000,"delta_pdef":8000,"has_alternative_image":1,"material_exp":1000,"name":{"en":"XX Judgement [Reverse]","ja":"XX 審判【逆位置】","ko":"XX 심판[역위치]","zh_hant":"XX 審判【逆位】"},"profile":{"en":"Stagnation, Regret, Separation","ja":"停滞、後悔、別れ","ko":"정체, 후회, 이별","zh_hant":"停滯、後悔、別離"},"published_at":1633330800,"rarity":4,"type":1,"_id_":4000189},"4000190":{"active_skill_id":46,"appearance_chara_ids":[202],"auto_skill1_id":22394,"auto_skill1_type":2,"base_atk":113,"base_hp":445,"base_mdef":363,"base_pdef":363,"can_use_limitbreak_item":1,"cost":12,"delta_atk":3000,"delta_hp":45000,"delta